Class QuestionReport

java.lang.Object
FBLAQuiz.QuestionReport

public class QuestionReport
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<QuestionReport>

Question Report Class

The Question Report Class creates a report that represents a question from a Quiz that was asked, and the answers to it. This object is intended to be created for a question only once it has been answered.
Author:
Varun Unnithan
